pageTitle: Busk8 celebrates busking on The Tube and Live8

title.title: Busk8 celebrates busking on The Tube and Live8

texts: Busk8 is a two-hour concert to celebrate the second year anniversary of London Underground's busking scheme and in support of Live8.
All proceeds to be donated to Make Poverty History campaign
#EndEditableBusk8 will see a group of talented Underground buskers perform at Canary Wharf station on Friday 1 July from 1000 to 1200.
All proceeds will be donated to the Make Poverty History campaign. Busk8 features a wide range of musical styles from Opera to Blues and RnB.
Busk8 will be presented by Sky Travel presenter Joanna Sinnott.
